comments[11]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-03-06T09:42:43.394Z",cursor-maintainer,Unknown capability names should be explicit diagnostics instead of silent no-ops.
  "2026-03-06T09:42:57.987Z",cursor-maintainer,"Planned changeset: update PRD/README capability contract to specify unknown-capability diagnostics, then implement deterministic extension_capability_unknown warnings in loader discovery and add regression assertions."
  "2026-03-06T09:57:36.333Z",cursor-maintainer,"Implemented docs-first hardening for unknown manifest capability names: PRD.md + README.md now specify deterministic extension_capability_unknown diagnostics; loader discovery now emits extension_capability_unknown:<layer>:<name>:<capability> warnings while preserving load/activation isolation; tests/unit/extension-loader.spec.ts now asserts unknown-capability warnings and non-blocking load behavior. Verification: pm test pm-hzh6 --run --timeout 7200 --json => linked_tests=2 passed=2 failed=0 skipped=0; pm test-all --status in_progress --timeout 7200 --json => items=1 linked_tests=2 passed=2 failed=0 skipped=0; pm test-all --status closed --timeout 7200 --json => items=85 linked_tests=255 passed=62 failed=0 skipped=193. Coverage evidence remains 100% lines/branches/functions/statements from linked coverage run."
  "2026-04-05T17:04:23.312Z",codex-agent,"Scope extended here for Issue #5 follow-up (warnings-only): improve unknown capability guidance with allowed-capability lists and nearest-match suggestions; no new extension lint command in this change set per approved scope. Duplicate-check evidence confirms this remains the canonical capability-diagnostics lineage."
  "2026-04-05T17:36:39.917Z",codex-agent,"Implemented warnings-only capability guidance hardening: unknown capability warnings now include allowed capability lists and nearest-match suggestions when confidence is high, and health/doctor surfaces include capability_guidance metadata plus remediation text referencing allowed capabilities. Verification: node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/unit/extension-loader.spec.ts tests/unit/extension-command.spec.ts tests/unit/health-command.spec.ts passed."
  "2026-04-05T17:56:40.284Z",codex-agent,"Evidence: full verification passed via node scripts/run-tests.mjs coverage (895 tests, branches 91.01%) and pnpm build; unknown capability warnings now include allowed list + nearest-match guidance and are surfaced in health/doctor outputs."
  "2026-04-05T18:46:10.787Z",codex-agent,Reopened for legacy capability alias/deprecation mapping and machine-readable capability contract metadata (version + alias map) in doctor/health diagnostics while preserving warning compatibility.
  "2026-04-05T19:29:05.878Z",codex-agent,"Completed capability contract remediation: legacy alias mapping (migration/validation -> schema), capability contract metadata surfaced in health/doctor, and docs synchronized across README/EXTENSIONS/ARCHITECTURE/PRD/CONTRIBUTING/CHANGELOG. Verification: node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/unit/extension-loader.spec.ts tests/unit/extension-command.spec.ts tests/unit/health-command.spec.ts tests/unit/completion-command.spec.ts tests/unit/pi-agent-extension.spec.ts tests/integration/cli.integration.spec.ts; node scripts/run-tests.mjs coverage; pnpm typecheck."
  "2026-04-05T20:39:49.181Z",codex-agent,Duplicate-check evidence refreshed; reusing canonical capability diagnostics lineage for alias-remap warning-noise remediation (no duplicate item created).
  "2026-04-05T20:46:36.702Z",codex-agent,"Progress: implemented legacy manifest capability alias remap (migration/validation -> schema) with consolidated extension_capability_legacy_alias warning, preserved unknown-capability diagnostics for truly unknown values, and updated doctor/health capability guidance parsing/remediation. Verification: node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/unit/extension-loader.spec.ts tests/unit/extension-command.spec.ts tests/unit/health-command.spec.ts passed."
