close_reason: Capability diagnostics hardening scope is complete and verified; item remained in progress despite completion evidence.
body: "Context: extension manifests now enforce declared known capabilities but unknown capability names are silently ignored. Approach: add deterministic discovery-time diagnostics for unknown capability names, document behavior, and cover with unit tests while keeping runtime failure isolation unchanged.\n\nFollow-up scope: improve extension capability diagnostics with explicit allowed capability lists and nearest-match suggestions in health/doctor details (warnings-only scope; no new extension lint command in this change set)."
